Developer Terms of Use
des:
Welcome to the Fart Quiz, a simple game where you listen to a fart and guess the tune, the skill is available on all devices but looks even better on screens. Try it today!

IMPORTANT: You can say Repeat at anytime to hear the Fart sounds again!

The goal of the quiz is to play as many fart packs as you can. The person with the highest score at the end of the month top's our leaderboard and is crowned the Maestro!

We also add new bonus packs through out the month so keep on checking in!
